\c 7
\s Zvipiriso zvinopiwa paaritari
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika nezuva Mozisi raakapedza naro kumisa tabhenakeri\x + Eki. 40.17,18. Rev. 8.10,11. Num. 6.10.\x*, uye aizodza\x + Eki. 40.17,18. Rev. 8.10,11. Num. 7.10.\x*, uye aiita tsvene, nenhumbi dzayo dzese, nearitari nemidziyo yayo yose, uye azvizodza nekuzviita zvitsvene,
\v 2 kuti machinda aIsraeri, misoro yeimba yemadzibaba avo, vaiva machinda emarudzi, vaiva vatariri pavakaverengwa\x + 1.4.\x*, ape \add zvibairo\add*.
\v 3 Ndokuuya nezvipo zvavo pamberi paJehovha, ngoro nhanhatu dzakafukidzwa\x + Isa. 66.20.\x*, nenzombe gumi nembiri; ngoro yemachinda maviri, uye nzombe pane umwe; ndokuuya nazvo pamberi petabhenakeri.
\v 4 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 5 Gamuchira kwavari, kuti zvive zvekubata basa retende rekusangana; uye uchazvipa kuVaRevhi, umwe neumwe zvichienderana nebasa rake.
\v 6 Naizvozvo Mozisi wakagamuchira ngoro nenzombe ndokuzvipa kuVaRevhi.
\v 7 Ngoro mbiri nenzombe ina wakapa kuvanakomana vaGerishoni zvichienderana nebasa ravo\x + 4.25,28.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino ngoro ina nenzombe sere wakapa kuvanakomana vaMerari zvichienderana nebasa ravo\x + 4.29,31,33.\x*, paruoko rwaItamari, mwanakomana waAroni mupristi.
\v 9 Asi kuvanakomana vaKohati haana kupa, nokuti basa renzvimbo tsvene raiva pamusoro pavo\x + 4.15.\x*, vautakure pamafudzi\x + 4.4-15; 2 Zvak. 6.13.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Machinda akapa zvekutsaurwa kwearitari nezuva rayakazodzwa naro\x + 7.84,88. Det. 20.5. 1 Madz. 8.63. 2 Makor. 7.5,9. Ezi. 6.16. Neh. 12.27.\x*; nemachinda akapa zvipo zvawo pamberi pearitari.
\v 11 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Muchinda umwe neumwe nezuva rake, vachapa zvipo zvavo zvekutsaurira aritari\x + 7.84,88. Det. 20.5. 1 Madz. 8.63. 2 Makor. 7.5,9. Ezi. 6.16. Neh. 12.27.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Neanopa chipo chake zuva rekutanga waiva Naashoni, mwanakomana waAminadhabhu, werudzi rwaJudha\x + 1.7\x*.
\v 13 Zvino chipo chake \add chaiva\add* ndiro huru yesirivha imwe, uremu hwayo \add mashekeri\add* zana nemakumi matatu\x + Eki. 30.13.\x*, ndiro yekusasa yesirivha imwe yemashekeri makumi manomwe, zvichienderana neshekeri reimba tsvene\x + Eki. 30.13.\x*; zviviri zvazvo zvizere neupfu hwakatsetseka hwakakanyiwa nemafuta, zvive chipo chechidyiwa\x + Rev. 2.1,4; Num. 8.8.\x*;
\v 14 mukombe umwe wegoridhe ye\add mashekeri\add* gumi, uzere nezvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira\x + Eki. 30.34.\x*,
\v 15 nzombe diki imwe mhuru yemombe, gondohwe rimwe, gwayana rimwe regore rimwe, zvive chipo chinopiswa\x + Rev. 1.2,3.\x*;
\v 16 mbudzana imwe yembudzi, ive chipo chezvivi\x + Rev. 4.23,24.\x*;
\v 17 uye zvechibairo chezvipo zvekuyananisa, nzombe mbiri, makondohwe mashanu, nhongo shanu dzembudzi, makwayana mashanu egore rimwe\x + Rev. 3.1.\x*; ichi chipo chaNaashoni, mwanakomana waAminadhabhu.
\p
\v 18 Nezuva repiri Netaneri, mwanakomana waZuwari, muchinda waIsasikari wakapa \add chipo\add*\x + 1.8.\x*.
\v 19 Wakapa chipo chake: Ndiro huru yesirivha imwe, uremu hwayo \add mashekeri\add* zana nemakumi matatu, ndiro yekusasa yesirivha imwe yemashekeri makumi manomwe, zvichienderana neshekeri reimba tsvene; zvose zviviri zvizere neupfu hwakatsetseka hwakakanyiwa nemafuta, zvive chipo chechidyiwa;
\v 20 mukombe umwe wegoridhe re\add mashekeri\add* gumi, uzere nezvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira;
\v 21 nzombe diki imwe mhuru yemombe, gondohwe rimwe, gwayana rimwe regore rimwe, zvive chipo chinopiswa;
\v 22 mbudzana imwe yembudzi, ive chipo chezvivi;
\v 23 uye zvechibairo chezvipo zvekuyananisa, nzombe mbiri, makondohwe mashanu, nhongo shanu dzembudzi, makwayana mashanu egore rimwe; ichi chipo chaNetaneri, mwanakomana waZuwari.
\p
\v 24 Nezuva retatu \add kwakauya\add* Eriabhu mwanakomana waHeroni muchinda wevana vaZebhuruni\x + 1.9.\x*.
