\v 84 Uku ndiko kwaiva kutsaurwa kwearitari\x + 7.11.\x* nezuva rayakazodzwa naro, nemachinda aIsraeri: Ndiro huru dzesirivha gumi nembiri, ndiro dzekusasa dzesirivha gumi nembiri, mikombe yegoridhe gumi nemiviri.
\v 85 Imwe neimwe ndiro huru yesirivha yaiva \add mashekeri\add* zana nemakumi matatu, uye imwe neimwe ndiro yekusasa \add mashekeri\add* makumi manomwe; sirivha yose yendiro yaiva \add mashekeri\add* zvuru zviviri nemazana mana, zvichienderana neshekeri reimba tsvene.
\v 86 Mikombe yegoridhe gumi nemiviri izere nezvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira, umwe neumwe waiva \add mashekeri\add* gumi, zvichienderana neshekeri reimba tsvene; goridhe rose remikombe raiva \add mashekeri\add* zana nemakumi maviri.
\v 87 Zvipfuwo zvose zvechipo chinopiswa \add zvaiva\add* nzombe diki gumi nembiri, makondohwe gumi nemaviri, makwayana egore rimwe gumi nemaviri, nechipo chazvo chechidyiwa; nembudzana dzembudzi gumi nembiri, zvive chipo chezvivi.
\v 88 Nezvipfuwo zvose zvechibairo chechipo chekuyananisa \add zvaiva\add* nzombe diki makumi maviri nena, makondohwe makumi matanhatu, nhongo dzembudzi makumi matanhatu, makwayana egore rimwe makumi matanhatu. Uku ndiko kwaiva kutsaurwa kwearitari\x + 7.11.\x*, shure kwekuzodzwa kwayo\x + 7.1,10.\x*.
\p
\v 89 Zvino Mozisi wakati apinda mutende rekusangana kutaura naye, wakanzwa inzwi richitaura naye\x + 12.8. Eki. 33.9,11.\x* kubva pamusoro pechigaro chengoni chaiva pamusoro peareka yechipupuriro kubva pakati pemakerubhi maviri; ndokutaura naye\x + Eki. 25.22.\x*.